          <p><kbd>Ctrl+O</kbd> — Open a file (MusicXML supported).</p>
          <p><kbd>Ctrl+S</kbd> — Save.</p>
          <p><kbd>Ctrl+Shift+H</kbd> — Browse file history (up to 50 snapshots of past edits).</p>
