        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Export formats</h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          <p><strong>MusicXML</strong> — compatible with MuseScore, Dorico, Sibelius, Finale, and any other notation app.</p>
          <p><strong>PDF</strong> — print-ready export of the full score or individual parts.</p>
          <p><strong>WAV</strong> — render your score to an audio file.</p>
          <p><strong>ABC Notation</strong> and <strong>LilyPond</strong> — copy to clipboard via the Command Palette.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
